#
if hasCondition trigger blacksmithzabin
	chat trigger "Zabin says: Have you smelted any ingots yet? Just toss the ores and some coal into the furnace to smelt an ingot."
	chat trigger "Zabin says: You need to supply me the ingots. I need 1 ingot of all 5 types of ore plus a template of the item you want. I'll craft any for you, 3k gp a piece."
	endscript
	end
# first meeting
chat trigger "Zabin says: I'm a blacksmith, and I can make God armor!"
chat trigger "Zabin says: My brother outside crafts pickaxes. There's 5 types of ore and I need 1 ingot of each kind of ore to make 1 item of God gear."
chat trigger "Zabin says: You need to supply me the ingots. I need 1 ingot of all 5 types of ore plus a template of the item you want. I'll craft any for you, 3k gp a piece."
addCondition trigger blacksmithzabin
endscript 

